overview.en: IDS（International distributed settlement system）Through the construction of the distributed settlement system framework,the traditional settlement system has a secure,scalable,flexible and pluggable service-oriented architecture.Greatly improve the businsee scalability,automation and computing power of the settlement system.
overview.zh: IDS（International distributed settlement system）国际分布式结算系统：通过分布式解算系统框架的构建，使传统解算系统具备了一个安全、可扩展、灵活、可插入的面向服务框架。大大提升了结算系统的业务延展性、自动化程度和计算能力
